N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 1, ch. IV, subch. A, pt. 165

Statutory authority: Agriculture and Markets Law, §§18, 156-c, 156-d, 156-f

The following standards are practically identical with
corresponding standards of potato grades heretofore promulgated by the

Secretary of Agriculture of the United States, commonly known as "U.S. Potato

Grades."
State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
